        <div class="intro__content">
            <p>Traditional stand-up meetings often become repetitive and dry. By introducing a small element of <strong>randomness and play</strong>, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Improve Engagement:</strong> Team members pay more attention when the speaking order is unpredictable.</li>
